# magik-repo vault
# Knowledge is git-tracked truth and IS committed. Memory is the agent's
# runtime log — per-runtime thought, never tracked. The line below keeps the
# memory mount out of git while the knowledge mount stays versioned.
__MEMORY_MOUNT__/

